  "text": "This instrument performed services and on Sunday night by channeling other members of the Confederation. We are reluctant to continue this because of the possibility for slipping into trance and being offered the services of the negatively polarized adept. Are there any safeguards to create a situation where she cannot go into trance other than a protected working such as this one? I and Raw. There are three. This would involve daily conscious and a serious thought. The hand may be held.",
